  help: Rhai runs in expression-only mode: no `fn`, no loops, no assignment. Predicates with string literals require KDL raw strings (`when=#"agent.phase == "review""#`) because Rhai also uses
        double quotes. `ark scene fmt` auto-promotes plain → raw when a predicate body contains `"`.
